To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private CoppockCurve _cc;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_cc = CC(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_cc.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "coppockcurve", _cc.Current.Value);
}
